The '''Corioline Marlee Theatre''' was a renowned theater and place of the arts that was located on [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] before that [[Planet/Legends|world's]] destruction. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] visited it in her youth; the rebuilt [[Grand Convocation Chamber]] of the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]] reminded her of the theater.

In 0 BBY, it was destroyed along with Alderaan itself.

